Musician, Kanye West sure knows how to make an entrance. On Sunday night, the 42-year-old star stepped out in Miami to debut his Mary opera at the Marine Stadium. The rapper was covered in silver paint on his entire face, paired with a silver outfit from top to bottom!. Ye took his onstage outfit to a whole other level as he literally was dripping in silver from head-to-toe. While it's unclear why he chose to paint his face silver and wear an all-silver metallic ensemble, it's safe to say it's going to be one unforgettable look. Twitter is already buzzing, his fans are asking to please stop, but the Rapper sipped on some champagne and carried on about his craft! Kanye's whole team was draped in silver garments.    